aa(lp94
VBut to be a great photojournalist,
p95
aVyou have to have more than just one or two
p96
aVgreat photographs in you.
p97
aVYou've got to be able to make them all the time.
p98
aVBut even more importantly,
p99
aVyou need to know how to create a visual narrative.
p100
aVYou need to know how to tell a story.
